Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:13.76,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,In my heart, I'm always, always drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:21.85,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,My very own world map, where my dreams come true
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.56,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,(Bamboo-copter!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:30.57,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,To fly through the sky, to cross time, to go to faraway countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:37.53,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}I wish I could open the door and hey, just go there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:39.03,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,(Anywhere-Door!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:46.79,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I forget all of these when I grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:54.72,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, let's try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:56.47,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharararara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.93,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.39,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,there's always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.72,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,a shining dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:04.23,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:10.44,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,With that pocket, make it come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.07,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Shararara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.40,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing a song...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.95,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,...and everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.37,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,...hold hands together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:19.45,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:28.25,TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Who throughout the world, makes dreams come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:38.07,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(417,303)}The Great Avalanche in my Room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the latest and greatest models of skis and snowboards on the market!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my skis are cool too, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My skis look pretty good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family planned to go skiing at our country house next weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so how about you guys come along too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Then we're all going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What's wrong, Nobita?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have skis, but it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. The problem is you don't want to come because you can't ski, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobita's always been terrible at sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Let's see if my dad'll buy me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does, I'll go ski too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Nobita! That's the way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go ski!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go! Of course I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4\fad(100,100)}I hope Dad doesn't want to buy them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We want to go ski, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you can't buy them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too expensive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna buy them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys! Can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to ski? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was starting to get worried since you show no interest in sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you finally decided to do some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case this ever happened, I'd already bought the skis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Nobita!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Nobita, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great, Nobita-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can come ski with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the best part will be seeing if you can ski at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm sure he'll be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, in the news they say there won't be a lot of snow in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the weather forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,In the next few days, there'll be a lot of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to all ski fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it? If the problem is you can't ski, just practice a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, there's no snow yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it when it snows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By then it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's looking forward to seeing me fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna lend me something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0120,,Portable Ski Track!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll allow you to practice skiing here in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, climb onto the mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how I'm skiing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The conveyor belt leans taking your speed into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can keep skiing as long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you change direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belt moves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belt stops too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun! Let me, let me, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First I climb onto the carpet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ski belt won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't working! It won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now that I stopped, the belt stopped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't want the others to laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be laughed at,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to get hurt even less!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't try in a place like this! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't try to ski unless you're in a place surrounded by snow as far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there's no inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use one of the options in the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! But how did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-dimensional projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're inspired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, start training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The belt's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you move, the background moves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fall, snow jumps around you like in a real track.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you stop, the background stops too. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it just like a real ski track?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make the snow cold, will you do it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to use this button, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Feeling up to it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It-it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said you'd ski if it was cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going for a scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. Put on this scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's practice, practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't like skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to do the same as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something doesn't go the way you want, you drop it right in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious. Stop running away and face up to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to stop making the same mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were that worried about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you cared so much about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you understand, it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll fall... err, I mean try, with everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That's the way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how little by little, you got better?\NIt's easier than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this skiing thing's more enjoyable by the minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine since you're exercising and all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to catch a cold here! {spanish dub had "My micro-chips are freezing up" but I think they were being a little liberal there}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bump up the temperature a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was that button...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I think I pressed the wrong button!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to make it {\i1}that{\i0} realistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even ski like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this! I'm going to freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away! The exit. Where's the exit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... But there was no option to make avalanches!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Doraemon was buried!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find help and save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My room isn't that big! And no matter how much I run, I can't find the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobi-{\i1}chan{\i0}? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Please, somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
